        "created_at": "2023-12-16T03:04:12.172Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I am new to this forum. Please welcome, me, Chris from Brooklyn. I tasted a 2019 organic CDP today that, as it opened up over the evening, had notes of barbeque sauce! I read through a previous thread here about mercaptins in wine, but didn\u2019t see quite what I was detecting today in this wine.</p>",
